

Automated Deployment of War file to Tomcat Server

Tools to be used : -
Ansible
Github
Jenkins


Prerequisites:-
3 Servers - Jenkins Server, Ansible Master and Tomcat Server to be node
2 repos - One repo to store playbook and other one for storing addressbook.war file


Hints

Ansible Playboook contents-
==========================
1) Clone the repo for address_book.war
2) Install and configure tomcat
3) Deploy address_book.war to tomcat server

Jenkins Job contents:-
======================
1) Clone the repo of playbook
2) run the ansible playbook with parameters as servername
